      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个时序图，展示用户在VSCode里打开.mmd文件后，Mermaid扩展是怎么工作的。核心参与者有四个：用户、VSCode本身、Mermaid扩展，还有Mermaid渲染引擎。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "VSCode",
        "Extension",
        "Mermaid"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，四个participant。我注意到您把扩展叫\"Extension\"，但具体是指Mermaid扩展对吧？还有Mermaid这里是指渲染引擎还是整个工具链？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Extension",
        "Mermaid"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Extension就是VSCode的Mermaid扩展插件，Mermaid是底层的渲染引擎。这样区分是为了看清调用链。第一步是用户打开.mmd文件，触发VSCode的响应。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "VSCode",
        ".mmd file"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把四个参与者和第一条消息加上：User指向VSCode，标注\"Open .mmd file\"。接下来是VSCode激活扩展？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "VSCode",
        "Open .mmd file"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "没错，VSCode检测到文件类型后，会向Extension发送激活指令。然后扩展把文件内容交给Mermaid引擎去解析，这一步很关键，是Extension到Mermaid的调用。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "VSCode",
        "Extension",
        "Mermaid",
        "Activate extension",
        "Parse diagram"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加：VSCode→Extension是\"Activate extension\"，Extension→Mermaid是\"Parse diagram\"。那解析完成后，数据怎么回流？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "VSCode",
        "Extension",
